{"words":[{"word":"manager","count":2},{"word":"always","count":2},{"word":"silva","count":2},{"word":"return","count":2},{"word":"opportunity","count":2},{"word":"new","count":2},{"word":"team","count":2},{"word":"tut","count":2},{"word":"lupa","count":2},{"word":"silvas","count":2},{"word":"star","count":2},{"word":"ephor","count":2},{"word":"fine","count":2},{"word":"skill","count":1},{"word":"speech","count":1},{"word":"gift","count":1},{"word":"domina","count":1},{"word":"julia","count":1},{"word":"hoped","count":1},{"word":"behave","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"bid","count":1},{"word":"reason","count":1},{"word":"earliest","count":1},{"word":"seems","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"ally","count":1},{"word":"daresay","count":1},{"word":"hopes","count":1},{"word":"dashed","count":1},{"word":"disappointing","count":1},{"word":"hint","count":1},{"word":"charm","count":1},{"word":"crowd","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"impress","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"confident","count":1},{"word":"chances","count":1},{"word":"winning","count":1},{"word":"championship","count":1},{"word":"love","count":1},{"word":"money","count":1},{"word":"stoop","count":1},{"word":"level","count":1},{"word":"dangerous","count":1},{"word":"question","count":1},{"word":"carefully","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"easily","count":1},{"word":"snuff","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"doubted","count":1},{"word":"talent","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"game","count":1},{"word":"cut","count":1},{"word":"chase","count":1},{"word":"finished","count":1},{"word":"augusta's","count":1},{"word":"swift","count":1},{"word":"decision","count":1},{"word":"sealed","count":1},{"word":"fate","count":1},{"word":"part","count":1},{"word":"regardless","count":1},{"word":"house","count":1},{"word":"banished","count":1},{"word":"deceived","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"violated","count":1},{"word":"contract","count":1},{"word":"deny","count":1},{"word":"handled","count":1},{"word":"silvas'","count":1},{"word":"sponsorship","count":1},{"word":"bough","count":1},{"word":"legions","count":1},{"word":"ensure","count":1},{"word":"damage","count":1},{"word":"career","count":1},{"word":"minimal","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"event","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"year","count":1},{"word":"ready","count":1},{"word":"squeeze","count":1},{"word":"augusta","count":1},{"word":"fiercest","count":1},{"word":"hunter","count":1},{"word":"grounds","count":1},{"word":"queen","count":1},{"word":"storm","count":1},{"word":"brewing","count":1},{"word":"septimont","count":1},{"word":"intend","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"shelter","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"For a manager, isn't the skill of speech always a gift?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Domina Julia Silva hoped you'd behave and return home. She bid that I reason with you at the earliest opportunity.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"But... it seems you've found yourself a new ally. I daresay her hopes are dashed.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"How disappointing. Not even a hint of charm when there's no crowd around to impress.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Feeling confident about this new team of yours? What do you think your chances are of winning the championship?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"No. I do love money, but I don't stoop to that level to get it.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Tut, tut, dangerous question, Lupa. Think carefully. The Silvas may have made you a star, but they can just as easily snuff that star out.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"I've never doubted your talent, but these are the rules of the game.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Let me cut to the chase. The Silvas are finished.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Ephor Augusta's swift decision sealed their fate. Don't tell me you had no part in this.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Regardless, House Silva has been banished. Even if they deceived you first, you still left their team without a word and violated your contract. You can't deny that.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Fine, then. I handled the Silvas' sponsorship of the Bough of Legions, and I can ensure the damage to your career is minimal. In return, I'll be your event manager for the next year.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Always ready to squeeze an opportunity, aren't you, Lupa?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"...Fine. We'll do it your way.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126},{"text":"Ephor Augusta, the fiercest hunter in the grounds, our queen. If there's a storm brewing in Septimont, I intend to find the right place to take shelter.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000126}]}